item.title: happy new years!!
item.description: here are some pictures of the haps from last night. it was fun. First I went and had a great dinner with some friends. and then matiss and I went and juggled at rhythm a really crazy drum circle nightclub. it was nuts and crowded. a lot of fun. then we went to watusi and hung out. it was great. tommie was the dj. nobody killed him and it was all good.
